Popular singer Paul Okoye aka Rudeboy has shared his view on one of the most important virtues to men. The PSquare twin, who has found love again in a 22-year-old lifestyle influencer, Ifeoma Ivy after getting divorced from his wife, Anita, said men consider respect a big deal particularly from their partners. He suggested while love was important to everyman, respect matters the most to them. The 41-year-old entertainer wrote: “For Men … Sometimes is not all about love. RESPECT… is all that matters !!!”